@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_togvmo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((tmp + 0.32 / tmp + 0.37)))
    v2 = ((0.15 + (tmp + 0.60 + v1 + 0.91)) / tmp)
    v1 = ((0.42 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.87)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.71) - (v0 + 0.69 - v1 + 0.51)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.07) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.67)) - 0.82)
    data[tid] = v0
